  <h3>Form input widths</h3>

  <p>Use these classes to constrain the width of form inputs. Unlike grid column widths, they do not apply a float. On mobile they expand to 100% width. See <a href="/design-system/components/text-input#fluid-width-inputs">fluid width inputs in the text input component</a> for more detail.</p>

  {{ summaryList({
    rows: [
      {
